			<details>
				<summary><h5>CSS</h5></summary>
			</details>
			<details>
				<summary><h5>Javascript</h5></summary>
			</details>
	</article>
	<article>
		<h2>¿Donde eh estudiado?</h2>
		<p>
			Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vitae, eligendi.
